title: Computer Science Illuminated 6th Edition

Authored by the award-winning Nell Dale and John Lewis, Computer Science Illuminatedâ€™s unique and innovative layered approach moves through the levels of computing from an organized, language-neutral perspective. Designed for the introductory computing and computer science course, this student-friendly Sixth Edition provides students with a solid foundation for further study, and offers non-majors a complete introduction to computing
